I am feeling sad because people around me are experiencing tragedy and I can’t help. I am resisting this so it makes me feel uneasy a lot.

I am feeling anxious because I have a lot to do and am not sure if I can get it all done. I feel like I have too much on my plate, but don’t want to give any of it up or let anyone down. I need to prioritize my time better.

I am worried that my kids are making choices that aren’t good for them. I don’t want to be overbearing, but I also don’t wan them to face the consequences of bad choices. I try t talk to them about it, but I don’t know if they are taking me seriously.

I am feeling accomplished today. I had a great talk with my son today and I think that we had a connection. He told me about some things he is dealing with and asked for advice I feel like he is moving in the right direction.
I am excited. I got a promotion at work and cannot wait to get started.  Think that I can make a big impact in this role and feel valued.

I am feeling uneasy. I have a big decision to make and I know that people will be disappoint no matter what I choose. I feel like I am being selfish if I choose what is best for me, but I also know that I need to think about myself sometimes too.
